{"tid":2330703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now新聞台：瑞典佛系抗疫失效","createTime":"2020-12-18T08:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T09:57:49.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7981886b1258fa8cab7ad468bea6a2ed87b9eebc","tid":2330703,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n【Now新聞台】歐洲新冠病毒疫情一直未見緩和，英國、荷蘭、德國等進一步收緊防疫措施，連之前以「佛系抗疫」著稱的瑞典都一改政策，頒令限制8人或以上的聚集，晚上10時後禁止賣酒，夜店要在晚上10時半後關門，這些措施前所未有。<br />\n瑞典的新冠病毒確診個案突破32萬，累計逾7500名病人死亡，因感染新冠病毒而住院病人數目屢創新高。<br />\n瑞典在疫情爆發期間，拒絕高壓式封城停擺，提倡靠民眾自律，保持社交距離，學習與病毒共存，所謂的「佛系抗疫」一度被推崇為高度文明的表現。<br />\n然而，隨著疫情越見嚴峻，感染和死亡人數節節攀升，原先的讚美再不復見。取而代之的是「鬆馳」、「縱容」、「無能」這類批評聲音。<br />\n瑞典當局原先預料，第二波疫情在秋季來臨，屆時會有一大部分人有免疫力。但現實不似預期，自9月開始，瑞典的感染人數便一直上升。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=416983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416983&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=96f4f88e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416983&h=8f33916e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=416983</a>"},{"pid":"22f2ca478ae79c2b65ed860a11cd651e1905164a","tid":2330703,"uid":49643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"國屍講兩句？"},{"pid":"f2271633d9440e26eb3b1875d1dc08f64f796847","tid":2330703,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"22f2ca478ae79c2b65ed860a11cd651e1905164a","tid":2330703,"uid":49643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"國屍講兩句？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5ee05f2edc9f3c263b21e5ff6da0df46ec0679","tid":2330703,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"唱衰北歐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左膠死左去邊唔幫口?"}]}